===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|珏|文|t1=pieces of jade|t2=tattoo; stripe|ls=ic}}. However, the component 珏 appears as a more conservative version [[玨]]. The original meaning was "mixed colours" with a reference to jade pieces, then it turned into "stripe, spot, mark".

===Etymology 1===
Either the same etymon as {{och-l|班}} or related to {{och-l|駁}}.

